  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create an alarm snare by rigging one or more noisy objects to a trip wire, pressure plate or manual trigger.</p><p>When you create an alarm snare, you designate a range between 100 to 500 feet at which it can be heard.</p><p>When a Small or larger creature enters the square, the snare makes a noise loud enough that it can be heard by all creatures in the range you designated.</p><p></p><p>Build DC: 15</p><p>Notice/Disable DC: 14</p><p>Toolkit Req to create/disable: Trappers kit</p>",
